json.title: Hidden Crypt of Storm Star
json.story: The crypt is situated on a remote coast. Lately a huge albino snake has made its home here.

notes.text: A lavishly decorated wooden gate on the northern wall.
Some gold hidden in a crack of the floor.
A smith, checking the content of a strongbox.
A battered basket with a crowbar, a spear and a leather armor in it.
A rusty clockwork machine, sounds the alarm when the lever is pulled.
A mosaic of a star pattern on the floor
A sculpture of an elf warlock, a holy quill in its hands.
